  <brief_title>Behavioral and Cognitive Therapies for Auditory Hallucination Management</brief_title>
  <acronym>AcceptVoice</acronym>
  <official_title>Behavioral and Cognitive Therapies for Auditory Hallucination Management: Effectiveness and Analysis of Change Processes Involved With Hallucinations in a Population Suffering From Chronic Psychosis</official_title>
