  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The present study wants to evaluate the efficacy of a short psychoeducational type group
      intervention and Cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT) 3rd wave on the severity of hallucinatory
      Acoustico-Verbal (HAV) symptomatology in patients with schizophrenia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
